-424037.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[This ancient Chinese megacity hides mysterious underground tunnels buried for over 4,000 years]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/130880903.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/this-ancient-chinese-megacity-hides-mysterious-underground-tunnels-buried-for-over-4000-years/articleshow/130880903.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/this-ancient-chinese-megacity-hides-mysterious-underground-tunnels-buried-for-over-4000-years/articleshow/130880903.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-07T11:13:04+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-130881259,imgsize-105650.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA['They found nothing': Jeffrey Epstein's alleged suicide note released]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/130878000.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[A federal judge has ordered the release of a handwritten note, purportedly from Jeffrey Epstein, found nearly five years after his death. The note, discovered by his former cellmate, contains the line, "It is a treat to be able to choose ones time to say goodbye." The document was unsealed after a request by The New York Times.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/they-found-nothing-jeffrey-epsteins-alleged-suicide-note-released/articleshow/130878000.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/they-found-nothing-jeffrey-epsteins-alleged-suicide-note-released/articleshow/130878000.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-07T09:05:21+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-130878037,imgsize-460646.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Tyler “sym” Porter cause of death: Twitch streamer and TSM Valorant pro killed during birthday trip]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/130873767.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Tyler Porter, a rising Valorant professional and Twitch streamer known as “sym,” tragically died in a car accident on May 5 while celebrating his 21st birthday. The former TSM player was widely respected for his viral Jett gameplay and competitive success. Fellow player Austen also reportedly died in the crash. Tributes from teammates, friends, and the esports community quickly flooded social media, remembering sym as a talented player and beloved friend with a bright future ahead.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/tyler-sym-porter-cause-of-death-twitch-streamer-and-tsm-valorant-pro-killed-during-birthday-trip/articleshow/130873767.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/tyler-sym-porter-cause-of-death-twitch-streamer-and-tsm-valorant-pro-killed-during-birthday-trip/articleshow/130873767.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-07T04:38:25+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Barsha Dutta</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-130873767,imgsize-27354.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[“Pretty easy to clear up”: Candace Owens questions Blake Neff over Erika Kirk TPUSA leadership video after Charlie Kirk death]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/130873355.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Candace Owens and Blake Neff publicly clashed on X over Charlie Kirk’s alleged succession video and TPUSA leadership controversy. Owens demanded proof that Charlie Kirk approved Erika Kirk as successor, while Neff accused Owens of spreading conspiracy-driven attacks against the organization after Kirk’s death.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/pretty-easy-to-clear-up-candace-owens-questions-blake-neff-over-erika-kirk-tpusa-leadership-video-after-charlie-kirk-death/articleshow/130873355.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/pretty-easy-to-clear-up-candace-owens-questions-blake-neff-over-erika-kirk-tpusa-leadership-video-after-charlie-kirk-death/articleshow/130873355.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-07T03:56:03+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Sehjal Gupta</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-130873338,imgsize-803881.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[What pushed Australia to reportedly cancel Sneako’s visa? streamer responds with bold clarification]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/130870707.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Streamer Nico Sneako became part of a major controversy after reports claimed Australia cancelled his visa and issued a lifetime ban. Australian minister Tony Burke reportedly took the action over concerns related to hateful content. Sneako denied being deported and said he voluntarily left Australia after finishing his South East Asia trip and meetings in Sydney and Melbourne.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/what-pushed-australia-to-reportedly-cancel-sneakos-visa-streamer-responds-with-bold-clarification/articleshow/130870707.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/what-pushed-australia-to-reportedly-cancel-sneakos-visa-streamer-responds-with-bold-clarification/articleshow/130870707.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-07T02:56:19+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Sehjal Gupta</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-130870712,imgsize-1941671.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Who is Jane Fonda? Ted Turner’s ex-wife who once called him her 'favorite ex-husband']]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/130869973.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/who-is-jane-fonda-cnn-founder-ted-turners-ex-wife-who-once-called-him-her-favorite-ex-husband/articleshow/130869973.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/who-is-jane-fonda-cnn-founder-ted-turners-ex-wife-who-once-called-him-her-favorite-ex-husband/articleshow/130869973.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-07T02:40:00+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-130870482,imgsize-168456.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Clavicular charged in shocking Everglades shooting stream, faces up to 1 year in jail]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/130870046.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Kick streamer Braden Eric Peters, also known as Clavicular, is in legal trouble. He is charged with unlawfully firing a gun in a public place. The incident occurred in the Florida Everglades during a livestream. Wildlife officials investigated the viral video. Peters' lawyers state he followed a guide's instructions and no harm occurred. The case highlights livestream consequences.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/clavicular-charged-in-shocking-everglades-shooting-stream-faces-up-to-1-year-in-jail/articleshow/130870046.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/clavicular-charged-in-shocking-everglades-shooting-stream-faces-up-to-1-year-in-jail/articleshow/130870046.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-07T02:06:06+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Sumit Roy</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-130870031,imgsize-464510.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA['Comparing H-1B workers...': Row over claim visa holders are less than 0.5% of US jobs]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/130869861.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/comparing-h-1b-workers-to-entire-workforce-row-over-us-entrepreneurs-claim-visa-holders-are-less-than-0-5-of-jobs/articleshow/130869861.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/comparing-h-1b-workers-to-entire-workforce-row-over-us-entrepreneurs-claim-visa-holders-are-less-than-0-5-of-jobs/articleshow/130869861.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-07T01:58:51+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-130869902,imgsize-189752.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Ted Turner and legacy of WCW: How he revolutionized wrestling, created nWo, and challenged Vince McMahon]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/130865695.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Ted Turner, the media mogul behind CNN, TNT, and TBS, has died at 87. He transformed professional wrestling by turning WCW into a national rival to WWF, launching Monday Nitro and the nWo era. Turner’s hands-off approach, cultural insight, and media empire permanently reshaped wrestling and television. He is survived by five children, 14 grandchildren, and two great-grandchildren.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/sports/international-sports/ted-turner-and-the-legacy-of-wcw-how-he-revolutionized-wrestling-created-nwo-and-challenged-vince-mcmahon/articleshow/130865695.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/sports/international-sports/ted-turner-and-the-legacy-of-wcw-how-he-revolutionized-wrestling-created-nwo-and-challenged-vince-mcmahon/articleshow/130865695.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-07T01:51:36+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI Sports Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-130869632,imgsize-657564.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[JasonTheWeen, Marlon, StableRonaldo under fire for running red light and stop sign on stream]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/130869450.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Popular streamers JasonTheWeen, Marlon, and StableRonaldo are facing backlash after a clip showed them disregarding traffic laws on motorized two-wheelers. The video captured them running a red light and failing to fully stop at a stop sign, with viewers also noting the absence of helmets. This incident has ignited discussions about streamer accountability and road safety.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/jasontheween-marlon-stableronaldo-under-fire-for-running-red-light-and-stop-sign-on-stream/articleshow/130869450.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/jasontheween-marlon-stableronaldo-under-fire-for-running-red-light-and-stop-sign-on-stream/articleshow/130869450.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-07T01:25:36+05:30</pubDate